Imali izosiza izitshudeni ebesezingazokwazi ukubhalisela ukufunda kwazo kwalo nyaka. Umkhankaso, i-#IMadeADoctor, usungulwe wumkhandlu obhekelele izitshudeni ezenza izifundo zobudokotela e-UKZN, iMedical Campus Representative Council (MCRC), ukuqoqa imali ezosiza izitshudeni ezifundela ubudokotela ezikweleta inyuvesi. Emasontweni amabili kuqale umkhankaso sekuqoqwe uR1 million ozosiza abafundi abawu-188 babhalise. Iphini likasihlalo weSAMA, uDkt Mvuyisi Mzukwa, uthe uphiko lwale nhlangano lodokotela abasanda kungena, iJunior Doctors’ Association lugqugquzele ukuthi kunikelelwe izitshudeni ezifundela ubudokotela. “Akubanga yisinqumo esinzima ukuthatha isinqumo sokunikela kulo mkhankaso ngoba kubalulekile ukuthi batshale imali ezosiza ekutheni umkhakha wobudokotela ukhule,” uDkt Mzukwa. Uthe banethemba lokuthi ukunikela kwabo kuzogqugquzela abanye abantu ukuthi belule isandla emkhankasweni osiza izitshudeni ezingakwazi ukukhokhela izifundo zazo. UXolisa Njapha weMCRC, uthe bajabule kakhulu ngomnikelo owenziwe yiSAMA owenze ukuthi bakwazi ukuqoqa imali enguR1 million esikhathini esingamasonto amabili. UXolisa noThanduxolo Dube, owenza unyaka wakhe wokugcina, bahamba phambili emkhankasweni wokuqoqa imali yokusiza izitshudeni. Uthe kusadingeka uR8 million ngaphezulu ukusula isikweletu sabafundi. USolwazi Busisiwe Ncama, iphini likashansela, obuye abe yinhloko yekolishi lesayensi ethinta ezempilo, uncome kakhulu isinyathelo seSAMA sokufaka isandla wathi lokhu kuzosiza ekutheni kube nesibalo esithe xaxa sodokotela abazothola iziqu zabo.